# Bartleby currently requires no environment variables.
# All processing happens client-side in the browser; no API keys are used.
#
# If server-side features are added later (e.g. Dropbox sync via Netlify
# Functions), document the required variables here. Remember:
# - Secrets must NEVER use the VITE_ prefix (they would be bundled into client JS)
# - Route secrets through Netlify Functions (process.env.*) instead
